    "date": "2024-07-31T18:48:38Z",
    "text": "Medicare Orthotics and Prosthetics Patient-Centered Care Act\n\nThis bill prohibits payment under Medicare for a prosthesis, custom-fabricated orthosis, or off-the-shelf orthotics that is\u00a0delivered via a\u00a0drop shipment (i.e., shipped to an individual who does not have training in how to properly fit or care for the device). It also specifically allows for payment of replacements of custom-fitted devices."
